How can you engage with the other humans on [3d] in a way which causes good things to happen and minimizes problems?

This page collects widely endorsed [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norm_(social) norms], rules, and heuristics for discussing, debating, editing, and otherwise interacting with other people on [3d]. Proposed changes & additions are mostly held on child pages, but may in some cases appear in the comments of this page.
